Main Function
Creates a powerpoint based on a topic. Pulls text and images from web and auto creates a powerpoint.

How it works
User puts in a topic.
Searches up topic and displays different sites.
User selects sites to be used as sources.
Scrapes the sites for info and adds that into x amount of slides chosen by user.
Can chose to add quotes or paraphrase.
Cites the website on a work cited slide.
Pulls images from site to display on slide.
Can add or remove own points to slides.
Can export to powerpoint, google slides, pdf, etc.